<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 06:09:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在以色列等待哈马斯回应之际，内塔尼亚胡再次强硬立场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-waits-for-hamas-response-netanyahu-hardens-his-stance-again/0000018d-e230-d972-a5bf-eb374d740000</link><description>哈马斯关于人质谈判进展的积极迹象可能表明以色列军事压力的影响，以及协议可能导致战争结束 ■ 以色列警察的行为就好像他们是本格维尔警察，而不是仅限特拉维夫</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 03:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-waits-for-hamas-response-netanyahu-hardens-his-stance-again/0000018d-e230-d972-a5bf-eb374d740000</guid></item><item><title>美国称人质协议达成“基本轮廓”后，以色列团队将前往卡塔尔进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-live/israeli-team-to-head-to-qatar-for-talks-after-u-s-says-basic-contours-for-deal-reached/0000018d-e290-d596-a9ef-e3b39f2c0000</link><description>总理办公室：以色列国防军向战争内阁提交了从战区撤离加沙平民的计划 ■ 陆军宣布 10 月 7 日被俘士兵死亡，另外两名士兵在加沙战斗中丧生 ■ 美国国家安全顾问表示，他对以色列的安全“有些担忧”战后加沙计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 03:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-live/israeli-team-to-head-to-qatar-for-talks-after-u-s-says-basic-contours-for-deal-reached/0000018d-e290-d596-a9ef-e3b39f2c0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党需要一项人质协议来决定其在黎巴嫩的政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-needs-a-hostage-deal-to-dictate-its-policies-in-lebanon/0000018d-e23b-d47b-a1af-fe7feec90000</link><description>纳斯鲁拉将与以色列的边境冲突与加沙战争联系起来的政策受到越来越多的反对，这意味着真主党领导人可能需要更多地关注重新获得对黎巴嫩政治进程的完全控制，并为真正重要的运动做准备——任命黎巴嫩真主党领导人。总统将维护该组织的地位及其武器</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 22:13:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-needs-a-hostage-deal-to-dictate-its-policies-in-lebanon/0000018d-e23b-d47b-a1af-fe7feec90000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争爆发两天后，以色列警察因殴打抗议者而受到讯问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-questioned-for-beating-a-protester-two-days-after-war-in-gaza-began/0000018d-e1fa-d596-a9ef-e3fb28400000</link><description>在示威期间拍摄的一段视频中，可以看到警长梅厄·苏伊萨(Meir Suissa)在特拉维夫基里亚综合大楼外推搡抗议者，其中包括一名年长的抗议者，他将其推倒在地</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 21:25:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-questioned-for-beating-a-protester-two-days-after-war-in-gaza-began/0000018d-e1fa-d596-a9ef-e3fb28400000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构以组建新政府为条件要求以色列撤军加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-authority-conditions-new-government-formation-to-israeli-gaza-withdrawal/0000018d-e1cb-d972-a5bf-ebcfa57a0000</link><description>巴解组织最近一直在讨论改变拉马拉政府的组成，以纳入哈马斯和其他组织。一位高级消息人士称，这一改变的一些条件包括“巴勒斯坦所有派别达成全国协议”以及以色列国防军停止对约旦河西岸城市的袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 21:24:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-authority-conditions-new-government-formation-to-israeli-gaza-withdrawal/0000018d-e1cb-d972-a5bf-ebcfa57a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡要求驱逐“主要囚犯”；以色列高级官员猛烈抨击总理的“表现”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-demands-to-deport-major-prisoners-freed-top-official-slams-pms-performances/0000018d-e200-d596-a9ef-e3b33e470000</link><description>以色列高级消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡是在美国、卡塔尔和埃及提出提案后才提出驱逐要求的，这使得谈判变得复杂。他警告说，即使这是一种谈判策略，他的表现也可能会造成损害。</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 21:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-demands-to-deport-major-prisoners-freed-top-official-slams-pms-performances/0000018d-e200-d596-a9ef-e3b33e470000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列警察加大对人质家属的暴力力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-25/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-police-are-ramping-up-violence-against-the-families-of-hostages/0000018d-e17a-df79-a5cd-e17e595a0000</link><description>昨晚的抗议活动引人注目，不仅因为警察暴力的强度，还因为安全部队开始采取激进反应的速度。这标志着以色列抗议运动的一个重要转折点。但问题是：为了谁？</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 20:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-25/ty-article/.highlight/why-israels-police-are-ramping-up-violence-against-the-families-of-hostages/0000018d-e17a-df79-a5cd-e17e595a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军宣布 10 月 7 日被带入加沙的以色列士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/idf-announces-death-of-israeli-soldier-killed-on-oct-7-and-taken-into-gaza/0000018d-e1c1-d47b-a1af-fff723210000</link><description>10 月 7 日，装甲兵士兵奥兹·丹尼尔 (Oz Daniel) 驾驶的坦克被哈马斯击中身亡。他的尸体被哈马斯带入加沙地带，目前仍被哈马斯扣留。军队首席拉比在检查了允许按照哈拉卡埋葬的调查结果后确定了他的死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 19:59:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/idf-announces-death-of-israeli-soldier-killed-on-oct-7-and-taken-into-gaza/0000018d-e1c1-d47b-a1af-fff723210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列阻止西岸和加沙国际援助非政府组织工作人员的工作签证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-blocks-work-visas-from-international-aid-ngo-workers-in-west-bank-and-gaza/0000018d-e195-df79-a5cd-e1bfa8600000</link><description>这种拒绝扰乱了许多参与向加沙居民提供医疗援助、食品和水的机构的运作，这些居民主要受到严重饥饿和脱水的影响。一些援助人员告诉国土报，他们担心这一决定背后有政治动机</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 19:38:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-blocks-work-visas-from-international-aid-ngo-workers-in-west-bank-and-gaza/0000018d-e195-df79-a5cd-e1bfa8600000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不是泽伦斯基。但他们确实有一个共同点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/as-war-in-ukraine-hits-a-milestone-zelenskyy-and-netanyahu-adapt-to-shifting-geopolitics/0000018d-e127-dc4b-a1cd-f12f943a0000</link><description>俄罗斯入侵乌克兰两周年是基辅和更远地区进行深刻反省的阴沉时刻。尽管几乎不可能比较乌克兰战争和以色列加沙战争，但以色列仍然应该吸收其中的战略影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 18:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/as-war-in-ukraine-hits-a-milestone-zelenskyy-and-netanyahu-adapt-to-shifting-geopolitics/0000018d-e127-dc4b-a1cd-f12f943a0000</guid></item><item><title>周二在密歇根州举行的民主党初选成为对拜登加沙战争立场的公投</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tuesdays-democratic-primary-in-michigan-becomes-referendum-on-bidens-gaza-war-stance/0000018d-e07c-d596-a9ef-e3ff41ee0000</link><description>由于密歇根州拥有规模庞大的阿拉伯裔美国人和穆斯林裔美国人社区，美国总统乔·拜登将了解他自 10 月 7 日以来的行动可能会对他 11 月连任的机会产生多大影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 18:16:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tuesdays-democratic-primary-in-michigan-becomes-referendum-on-bidens-gaza-war-stance/0000018d-e07c-d596-a9ef-e3ff41ee0000</guid></item><item><title>美国称人质协议已达成“基本轮廓”；内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯的要求表示怀疑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/u-s-says-basic-contours-of-hostage-deal-reached-netanyahu-unclear-if-it-will-emerge/0000018d-e13d-dc4b-a1cd-f13dfc220000</link><description>美国国家安全顾问表示，以色列、埃及、卡塔尔和美国已就协议的初步条件达成一致；内塔尼亚胡表示，如果达成协议，以色列国防军对拉法恩的突袭计划将“有所推迟”</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 18:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/u-s-says-basic-contours-of-hostage-deal-reached-netanyahu-unclear-if-it-will-emerge/0000018d-e13d-dc4b-a1cd-f13dfc220000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 142 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-142/0000018d-e13d-df79-a5cd-e13feb7c0000</link><description>卡塔尔将主办以色列-哈马斯会谈，以达成新的人质释放/停火协议 ■ 哈马斯高级官员：对可能达成新协议的乐观情绪“并不反映现实” ■ 据报道，两名真主党成员在以色列对叙利亚-黎巴嫩边境的空袭中丧生 ■ WH ：拜登总统尚未看到或获悉以色列在拉法进行军事行动的任何计划 ■ 这是战争开始 142 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 17:49:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-142/0000018d-e13d-df79-a5cd-e13feb7c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长因发现获奖者抗议司法政变而取消了以色列科学奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-axed-israel-prize-category-upon-finding-winner-protested-judicial-coup/0000018d-e118-d596-a9ef-e3bbb3520000</link><description>尽管取消奖项类别的决定是十天前宣布的，但教育部长在得知评委会选择了科学领域的以色列科技巨头埃亚尔·瓦尔德曼(Eyal Waldman)后，几周前就做出了决定。他是反对内塔尼亚胡司法政变的主要抗议者</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 17:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-axed-israel-prize-category-upon-finding-winner-protested-judicial-coup/0000018d-e118-d596-a9ef-e3bbb3520000</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》坚称以色列撤回对加沙摄影师 10 月 7 日照片的“虚假指控”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/nty-insists-israel-withdraw-false-accusations-against-gaza-photographer-for-oct-7-images/0000018d-e0e4-dc4b-a1cd-f1ed84d00000</link><description>在以色列指控加沙摄影记者参与哈马斯对以色列南部的袭击后，《纽约时报》致函以色列驻纽约领事馆，声称所报道的指控是“虚假的”和“鲁莽的”</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 16:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/nty-insists-israel-withdraw-false-accusations-against-gaza-photographer-for-oct-7-images/0000018d-e0e4-dc4b-a1cd-f1ed84d00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列黑豹党创始人、前议员查理·比顿去世，享年 76 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/founder-of-israels-black-panthers-and-former-mk-charlie-biton-dies-at-76/0000018d-e07d-d596-a9ef-e3ff5ebe0000</link><description>比顿是摩洛哥卡萨布兰卡人，为以色列米兹拉希犹太人的权利而奋斗。他创立的组织成为米兹拉希左翼运动，将种族和阶级斗争结合起来，寻求建立巴勒斯坦国</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 14:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/founder-of-israels-black-panthers-and-former-mk-charlie-biton-dies-at-76/0000018d-e07d-d596-a9ef-e3ff5ebe0000</guid></item><item><title>男子在阿拉伯以色列城市被枪杀，疑有犯罪动机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-arab-israeli-city-suspected-criminal-motive/0000018d-e062-dc4b-a1cd-f16f88730000</link><description>三名30多岁的男子在枪击事件中受重伤。警方追捕并逮捕了两名试图驾车逃跑的嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 14:19:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-arab-israeli-city-suspected-criminal-motive/0000018d-e062-dc4b-a1cd-f16f88730000</guid></item><item><title>“这将带出更多人”：警察暴力标志着反内塔尼亚胡抗议者的转折点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/police-violence-marks-turning-point-for-anti-netanyahu-protesters/0000018d-df99-d47b-a1af-dfffa7320000</link><description>一名抗议者说，有些年轻人在加沙呆了四个月后回来了，水枪并没有吓到他们。许多人认为，警方的升级行动将迫使人们逃离家园，走上街头</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 12:32:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/police-violence-marks-turning-point-for-anti-netanyahu-protesters/0000018d-df99-d47b-a1af-dfffa7320000</guid></item><item><title>“将加沙的阿拉伯人转移到爱尔兰”：前美国犹太间谍波拉德支持以色列极右翼本格维尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/send-gazans-to-ireland-ex-spy-pollard-looks-to-ben-gvir-to-find-his-political-future/0000018d-dfe1-df79-a5cd-ffffa32f0000</link><description>波拉德表示，本-格维尔的“心是对的”，现在正在考虑在下次选举中以奥兹玛·耶胡迪特的名义竞选</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 11:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/send-gazans-to-ireland-ex-spy-pollard-looks-to-ben-gvir-to-find-his-political-future/0000018d-dfe1-df79-a5cd-ffffa32f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的加沙“后天”计划不可行，也不是一个计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-day-after-plan-for-gaza-is-part-of-his-last-gamble-to-hold-onto-power/0000018d-df9b-df79-a5cd-ffbfaa410000</link><description>以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周五秘密公布的战后加沙计划是一系列单方面声明，几乎不值得认真审查</description><pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 10:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-day-after-plan-for-gaza-is-part-of-his-last-gamble-to-hold-onto-power/0000018d-df9b-df79-a5cd-ffbfaa410000</guid></item></channel></rss>